assets.description:
Very rough model of the spine for Bad Juju.

Spine is 8' of 1" x .0623" square tubing. Rib attachments are mounted at about 15 degrees every 2' and drilled for 1/4" lateral bolts.

Central tube should be run through a roller to create a very gentle S-curve.

assets.description:
3D VR Immersive Sculpture

Statement:
 
Virtual sculptures are produced through Google Tilt Brush and Oculus Rift. It's dealing with the hands gestures in virtual space and the virtual textures and even keywords. Everything is focused on energy and flux. At the time of the post internet, the post media, the post sculpture and post painting. Virtual Reality is a way to question all of these practices.
 
Valéry Grancher 2017
